The Project uses the version 1.9.13, not version 2.
* JsonAutoDetect and Visibility
Control which fields and methods can be used for serialization and deserialization.

* Mix-in class
Change the way of serializing and deserializing existing classes 
or make it possible for unmodifiable classes to be serialized or deserialized.

* Global configuration for ObjectMapper using Module or SimpleModule with SetupContext
Implement or override their methods to globally customize the various kinds of configuration like

Learning Resources:
1. Github
https://github.com/FasterXML/jackson

2. Wiki Documentation for both older version 1.0+ and current version 2+ 
http://wiki.fasterxml.com/JacksonHome

3. Current Documentation
https://github.com/FasterXML/jackson-docs

